"<h1>Vol Surprise (GARCH) -- Sharpe 1.18 -- PASS</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>The paper uses an ADCC-EGARCH framework to model conditional volatility and dynamic correlations across global futures markets. The extracted tradeable factor is <strong>vol_surprise</strong>: the ratio of GARCH(1,1) conditional volatility to realized volatility. When GARCH overestimates volatility relative to what actually materializes (high vol_surprise ratio), it signals a calmer-than-expected market environment favorable for trending behavior. The strategy goes <strong>long commodities with high vol_surprise</strong> and short those with low vol_surprise, exploiting the cross-sectional dispersion in volatility regime mismatch.</p>\n<p>The economic intuition is rooted in the paper's finding that GARCH persistence (beta &gt; 0.9) dominates across all markets, meaning conditional variance is \"sticky\" while realized vol reacts faster. When the conditional/realized ratio is elevated, the market has recently calmed but the GARCH model hasn't caught up -- this identifies trending environments.</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.02</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3330</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>3.12</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.71 / 1.48</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.8</span></td><td>0.27</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.04</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.7</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.28</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.51</span></td><td>0.48</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.2</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.49</span></td><td>0.45</td><td>1.51</td><td>0.92</td><td>1.29</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.96</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>58</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3332</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>Round</th><th>Best Sharpe</th><th>Action</th><th>Effect</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>1.16</td><td>Initial 6-variant grid: GARCH/EWMA x rvol(60/120) + GJR + combo. Evidence gate failed.</td><td>GARCH variants strong (1.16), EWMA weak (-0.50 to 0.21).</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>1.16</td><td>Fixed evidence gate by extracting paper evidence (EGARCH formula, Table 3 results). Activated cs/ts normalization.</td><td>All gates passed. cs normalization added value (0.98).</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>1.18</td><td>Focused on GARCH winners. Grid: hold_days {5,10,20} x ic_gate {on/off} x GJR-120d. Dropped EWMA.</td><td>20d hold improved Sharpe 1.16-&gt;1.18, halved turnover 1.57-&gt;0.70. IC gate slightly helped.</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>RVOL_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>max(RVOL_WINDOW // 3, 1)</code></td><td>match polars ts_realized_vol default</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.8546</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 8.53s</li>\n</ul>"}